description: The positive test came from a resident who had recently returned to the island, the government said.
title: Coronavirus: Isle of Man sees first Covid-19 case in 109 days
title_page: Coronavirus: Isle of Man sees first Covid-19 case in 109 days - BBC News
maintext: Mr Quayle said he hoped the positive test would prove to be a "wake up call" for those who had returned to the island and "were tempted to break the rules" around self-isolation.
